{"ID":270311, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"311\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs310.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs312.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 311<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">themselves, and they are their own accusers. &ldquo;But,&rdquo; says one, &ldquo;I believe in one universal heaven and\n  hell, where all go, and are all alike, and equally miserable or equally happy.&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">What! where all are huddled together&mdash;the honorable, virtuous, and murderers, and\n  whoremongers, when it is written that they shall be judged according to the deeds done in the body?<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span>\n  But St. Paul informs us of three glories and three heavens.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> He knew a man that was caught up to\n  the third heavens.<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> Now, if the doctrine of the sectarian world, that there is but one heaven, is true,\n  Paul, what do you tell that lie for, and say there are three? Jesus said unto His disciples, &ldquo;In my\n  Father&rsquo;s house are many mansions, if it were not so, I would have told you. I go to prepare a place\n  for you, and I will come and receive you to myself, that where I am ye may be also.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Men of God Endowed with Wisdom<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Any man may believe that Jesus Christ is the Son of God,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> and be happy in that belief, and yet\n  not obey his commandments,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and at last be cut down for disobedience to the Lord&rsquo;s righteous\n  requirements.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">A man of God<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> should be endowed with wisdom, knowledge,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> and understanding, in order to\n  teach and lead the people of God.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> The sectarian priests are blind, and they lead the blind, and they\n  will all fall into the ditch together.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> They build with hay, wood, and stubble,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> on the old revelations,\n  without the true priesthood or spirit of revelation. If I had time, I would dig into hell, hades, sheol,\n  and tell what exists there.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Doctrine of the Godhead<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">There is much said about God and the Godhead.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> The scriptures say there are Gods many and\n  Lords many, but to us there is but one living and true God,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> and the heaven of heavens<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> could not\n  contain him;<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> for he took the liberty to go into other heavens. The teachers of the day say that the\n  Father is God, the Son is God, and the Holy Ghost is God, and they are all in one body and one\n  God.<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> Jesus prayed that those that the Father had given him out of the world might be made one in\n  them, as they were one [one in spirit, in mind, in purpose].<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> If I were to testify that the Christian\n  world were wrong on this point, my testimony would be true.<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109653\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109653)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109653)\">2 Cor. 5:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109604\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109604)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109604)\">1 Cor. 15:40-41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109695\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109695)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109695)\">2 Cor. 12:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109696\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109696)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109696)\">2 Cor. 12:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108793\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108793)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108793)\">John 14:2-3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107893\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107893)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107893)\">Matt. 7:21-23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108142\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108142)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108142)\">Matt. 21:28-31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108165\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108165)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108165)\">Matt. 23:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108516\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108516)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108516)\">Luke 12:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114035\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114035)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114035)\">D&amp;C 56:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109997\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109997)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109997)\">1 Tim. 3:1-7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110032\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110032)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110032)\">1 Tim. 6:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110075\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110075)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110075)\">2 Tim. 3:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110367\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110367)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110367)\">James 3:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111697\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111697)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111697)\">Mosiah 23:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108053\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108053)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108053)\">Matt. 15:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108466\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108466)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108466)\">Luke 6:39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109450\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109450)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109450)\">1 Cor. 3:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109138\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109138)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109138)\">Acts 17:29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109233\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109233)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109233)\">Rom. 1:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109907\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109907)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109907)\">Col. 2:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109476\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109476)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109476)\">1 Cor. 8:5-6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106291\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106291)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106291)\">Deut. 10:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106567\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106567)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106567)\">Neh. 9:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106438\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106438)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106438)\">1 Kgs. 8:27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106514\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106514)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106514)\">2 Chr. 2:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106519\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106519)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106519)\">2 Chr. 6:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109798\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109798)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109798)\">Eph. 4:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109991\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109991)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109991)\">1 Tim. 2:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111335\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111335)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111335)\">2 Ne. 31:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111621\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111621)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111621)\">Mosiah 15:2-6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112790\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112790)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112790)\">Morm. 7:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113357\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113357)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113357)\">D&amp;C 20:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115773\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115773)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115773)\">D&amp;C 121:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108874\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108874)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108874)\">John 17:9-11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108684\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108684)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108684)\">John 5:31 (JST)<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}